@startuml
hide footbox

skinparam backgroundColor transparent
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam ArrowColor #5a7088
skinparam SequenceLifeLineBorderColor #5a7088
skinparam SequenceLifeLineBackgroundColor #f7fbff
skinparam ParticipantBorderColor #4d6a86
skinparam ParticipantBackgroundColor #f7fbff
skinparam ParticipantFontColor #1f2f3d
skinparam NoteBorderColor #96a7b8
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #fffdf3

participant Primary as P
participant Secondary as S

== Remote busy ==

P -> S: I-frame
P -> S: I-frame (P=1)
note left: T1 starts

S --> P: RNR (F=1)
note right: peer not ready
note left: remote busy set\nTX I-frames suspended\nT1 stopped

... Primary polls periodically ...

P -> S: RR (P=1)
note left: T1 starts

S --> P: RNR (F=1)
note right: still not ready
note left: T1 stopped

P -> S: RR (P=1)
note left: T1 starts

S --> P: RR (F=1)
note right: peer ready again
note left: remote busy cleared\nTX I-frames resumed\nT1 stopped\nT3 started

P -> S: I-frame
P -> S: I-frame

@enduml
